### Peticiones de prueba para la API (Java / Spring Boot)
### Usa la extension "REST Client" de VS Code, o copia los curl.

@base = http://localhost:4000/api

### Salud
GET {{base}}/health

### --- Usuarios y roles ---
### (Por ahora SIN login; proteger para ADMIN cuando se agregue autenticacion)
GET {{base}}/users

### Crear usuario (roles: ADMIN | MANAGER)
POST {{base}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Lopez",
  "email": "maria@negocio.com",
  "password": "clave123",
  "role": "MANAGER"
}

### Cambiar rol / desactivar usuario
# PATCH {{base}}/users/<ID>
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# { "role": "ADMIN", "active": false }

### --- Categorias ---
GET {{base}}/categories

### Crear categoria
POST {{base}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Bebidas" }

### --- Productos ---
### Cada producto lleva su propia presentacion (texto), precio y stock.
GET {{base}}/products?page=1&pageSize=20

### Crear producto
POST {{base}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Corona",
  "presentation": "Botella 355ml",
  "cost": 18,
  "price": 35,
  "stock": 120
}

### Ajustar stock (resta 3)
# POST {{base}}/products/<PRODUCT_ID>/adjust-stock
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# { "delta": -3, "reason": "merma" }

### --- Ventas (futuro POS) ---
### Se vende un producto y descuenta su stock.
# POST {{base}}/sales
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# { "paymentMethod": "cash", "items": [ { "productId": "<PRODUCT_ID>", "quantity": 2 } ] }

### --- Facturas ---
GET {{base}}/invoices?from=2026-06-01&to=2026-06-30

### Registrar una factura (subida manual)
POST {{base}}/invoices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceDate": "2026-06-18",
  "vendor": "Distribuidora del Norte",
  "amount": 4500.00,
  "number": "A-12345",
  "notes": "Recompra de inventario"
}

### Buzon de correo (BASE: la otra persona conecta Mailgun/SES y el guardado en S3)
# POST {{base}}/invoices/email-inbound

### --- Contabilidad ---
GET {{base}}/accounting/weeks

### Crear semana
POST {{base}}/accounting/weeks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weekStart": "2026-06-08",
  "weekEnd": "2026-06-14",
  "revenue": 8000,
  "cost": 4500
}

### Resumen del reparto de una semana
# GET {{base}}/accounting/weeks/<ID>/summary

### Agregar reparto
# POST {{base}}/accounting/weeks/<ID>/allocations
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# { "type": "SALARIES", "label": "Sueldos", "amount": 1500 }
